These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade, tea, cola, iced-tea, sprite, water
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: sunflower, iris, daisy, bellflower, lily, rose, dahlia
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, skateboard, snowmobile, subway, train, van
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking tea is the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the skateboard is the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is the person drinking iced-tea##1
11. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
12. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
14. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |     3     |     4     |      5       |     6      |     7      |
| Beverage        | cola | tea     | sprite | lemonade | coffee      | water | iced-tea       |
| Flower       | iris        | daisy   | sunflower   | dahlia    | rose | bellflower    | lily     |
| Transport   | airplane    | skateboard | van       | train     | helicopter   | subway     | snowmobile |

