.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-2::.
7 different games are played: poker, backgammon, domino, mah-jongg, billiard, go, whist
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, mah-jonggsy, horror, mystery, satire, zombie
The people have 7 different hobbies: dancinging, drawing, dancing, photography, video-games, filmmaking, chess
 1. the person playing domino is the person watching horror movies##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is dancinging is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancinging is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person playing go##1
13. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person playing poker##1
14. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
15. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
16. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |     4     |   5    |   6    |   7    |
| Game      | whist  | poker     | mah-jongg  | billiard  | domino   | backgammon | go   |
| Movie-Genre   | mah-jonggsy | mystery | zombie | animation | horror | satire | comedy |
| Hobby           | dancing    | filmmaking   | photography  | chess    | video-games | dancinging   | drawing    |

