.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, avocado, blueberry, lemon, pomegranate, strawberry, zucchini
City: rome, new-york, venice, prague, edinburgh, hamburg, marseilles
7 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, backgammon, bridge, domino, monopoly, chess
 1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is the person playing chess##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
10. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
12. the person eating lemon is in the middle##1
13. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
14. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
15. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
16. the person traveling to rome is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Food    | pomegranate | blueberry | zucchini | lemon | apple      | avocado | strawberry |
| City     | rome         | marseilles     | venice   | edinburgh | new-york        | hamburg  | prague       |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | monopoly     | chess  | bridge  | snooker | domino  | backgammon   |

