The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, comedy, documentary, epic, spy, zombie
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, disco, hip-hop, ambient, pop, salsa, metal
 1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the manager is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of metal is the teacher##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the left of the designer##1
 7. the teacher is the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is the project-manager##1
 9. the librarian is the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
11. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
12. the person watching zombie movies is the librarian##1
13. the dressmaker is on the right of the fan of pop##1
14. the librarian is the fan of ambient##1
15. the dressmaker is the fan of hip-hop##1
16. the fan of trance is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |    5    |   6   |     7     |
| Job         | dancer    | librarian | teacher | designer | dressmaker | project-manager | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | zombie      | adventure   | documentary  | spy     | epic  | comedy    |
| Music-Genre           | trance | ambient       | metal         | pop       | hip-hop    | salsa | disco      |

