.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-7::.
There 7 different types of food: zucchini, garlic, peas, cabbage, radish, tomato, raspberry
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, chef, entrepreneur, manager, nurse, project-manager, teacher
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, november, september, june, april, january, may
 1. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is the chef##1
 3. the person eating peas is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the chef is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the analyst##1
 7. the person eating peas is the manager##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is the nurse##1
 9. the analyst is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
11. the person eating garlic is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
12. the teacher is on the left of the analyst##1
13. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person eating radish##1
14. the nurse is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
15. the person eating cabbage is the teacher##1
16. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |        3        |    4    |      5      |      6       |    7    |
