7 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, rat, fish, rabbit, guinea-pig, goldfish
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the wooden house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 6. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the modern house is on the far left##1
 9. the palace house is the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person eating corn is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
11. the owner of the rat is the wooden house##1
12. the person eating peach is on the left of the tower house##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
14. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating banana##1
15. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |       2        |    3    |    4    |     5      |       6       |     7      |
