.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-16::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, airplane, helicopter, jet-ski, tram, subway
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, coffee, fanta, iced-tea, milk, 7up
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, family, fantasy, satire, spy, time-travel
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
10. the person driving the subway is the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the airplane is the person watching fantasy movies##1
14. the person watching spy movies is the person driving the bus##1
15. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
16. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4     |      5      |      6      |     7      |
| Transport          | tram    | quad-bike | bus  | jet-ski | helicopter | subway     | airplane    |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate    | 7up  | coffee | iced-tea | milk       | fanta    | soy-milk |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | family  | spy      | animation | satire      | time-travel | fantasy    |

