.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-17::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: iris, tulip, amaryllis, sunflower, azalea, poppy, balloon-flower
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, d&b, reggae, dubstep, hip-hop, metal, jazz
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, handball, ice-hockey, sailing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is the fan of metal##1
 3. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
 5. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1
 6. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the person who growspoppy is the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
12. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
13. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
14. the person who growssunflower is the person who's sport is basketball##1
15. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the fan of metal##1
16. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |     7     |
| Flower    | poppy | tulip  | iris       | balloon-flower | sunflower    | azalea | amaryllis     |
| Music-Genre     | d&b     | hip-hop | reggae | dubstep | jazz | classical   | metal     |
| Sport   | handball   | sailing    | ice-hockey  | skiing     | basketball   | water-polo  | badminton |

