.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-18::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, chef, doctor, entrepreneur, firefighter, lawyer, project-manager
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, may, august, march, july, february, june
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, montecristo, aristoff, bongani, baccarat, game, cain
 1. the chef is in the middle##1
 2. the firefighter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the doctor is the aristoff-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the chef##1
 6. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the entrepreneur is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 9. the project-manager is on the left of the lawyer##1
10. the architect is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
12. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the game-smoker is on the left of the chef##1
14. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
15. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
16. the project-manager is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |   2    |     3     |     4     |      5      |      6       |    7    |
| Job           | project-manager | lawyer | architect | chef      | firefighter | entrepreneur | doctor  |
| Birthday   | february          | august  | june    | may | october     | july        | march |
| Cigar     | bongani         | baccarat | game      | cain     | blend        | montecristo          | aristoff     |

