.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-19::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: iris, daffodil, tulip, marigold, zinnia, balloon-flower, poppy
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, superhero, crime, epic, zombie, fantasy, animation
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, handball, rowing, rugby, soccer, swimming, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person who growsiris is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching zombie movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
11. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
12. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
13. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
14. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
15. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2        |     3     |     4      |    5     |     6      |     7      |
| Flower     | marigold   | poppy | zinnia | balloon-flower  | iris     | daffodil      | tulip |
| Movie-Genre     | family        | fantasy          | crime      | epic | animation    | superhero | zombie    |
| Sport   | volleyball | soccer         | handball  | basketball | swimming | rugby      | rowing     |

