.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-20::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: sudoku, baking, fishing, rock-climbing, collecting, reading, writing
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, british, chinese, indian, japanese, malaysian
7 different games are played: backgammon, whist, billiard, snooker, go, domino, canasta
 1. the person playing whist is on the right of the japanese##1
 2. the argentine is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 4. the australian is on the far right##1
 5. the british is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the indian is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
12. the person playing whist is on the left of the british##1
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the indian##1
14. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
15. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
16. the person who's hobby is writing is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |     6      |     7      |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing | fishing | baking     | sudoku       | writing       | reading     | collecting   |
| Nationality   | indian   | chinese  | argentine | japanese   | malaysian | british    | australian |
| Game     | canasta    | backgammon     | billiard | go | whist       | snooker | domino       |

 